comment: A sequence, S, consisting of the natural counting digits (A007376) interleaved with S.
Fractal sequence (Kimberling-type) based upon the counting digits.
Similar to but different from A025480 - _N. J. A. Sloane_, Nov 26 2020.
xref: First differs from A025480 at a(20).
